OL,3,CButchers to stay shut after severe rat
OL,4,Cinfestation found
OL,6,FA butchers in Wiltshire will remain
OL,7,Fshut after a severe rat infestation
OL,8,Fwas discovered during a food hygiene
OL,9,Finspection by Swindon Borough
OL,10,FCouncil's Environmental Health team.
OL,12,FA Hygiene Emergency Prohibition Order
OL,13,Fwas given to Kenya Halal Butchers, by
OL,14,Fmagistrates after being presented with
OL,15,Fevidence of the inspection at a
OL,16,Fhearing on Friday 8 March.
