OL,3,CButchers to stay shut after severe rat
OL,4,Cinfestation found
OL,6,FThe court heard when council officers
OL,7,Fvisited the premises on 28 February
OL,8,F2024, they immediately noticed the
OL,9,Fpoor standard of cleaning throughout
OL,10,Fthe store.
OL,12,FOfficers saw evidence that rats had
OL,13,Fbeen on the shop floor as they found
OL,14,Fready-to-eat foods, like peanuts and
OL,15,Fwalnuts, with gnawed shell casings
OL,16,Fsurrounding them.
OL,18,FFood packaging which had sellotape
OL,19,Fover the gnawed holes was also found
OL,20,Fat the shop on Bridge Street.
