OL,3,CButchers to stay shut after severe rat
OL,4,Cinfestation found
OL,6,FLarge quantities of rat droppings were
OL,7,Fdiscovered in front of the meat
OL,8,Fcounter under boxes of crips packets,
OL,9,Funder the refrigerated meat counter
OL,10,Fand under disused display counters.
OL,12,FNesting material had been taken from
OL,13,Faround the shop by the rodents,
OL,14,Fincluding insulation material from
OL,15,Fpipework, blue customer shopping bags
OL,16,Fand large quantities of food items
OL,17,Fsuch as black eye beans which the rats
OL,18,Fhad used to make a nest in the meat
OL,19,Fcounter.
