OL,3,CButchers to stay shut after severe rat
OL,4,Cinfestation found
OL,6,FThe officers commented that the smell
OL,7,Fof rat urine behind the meat counter
OL,8,Fwas disgusting.
OL,10,FThe court was told that the store was
OL,11,Falso extremely untidy with a large
OL,12,Famount of boxes, unused equipment and
OL,13,Fitems like a cement mixer being stored
OL,14,Fin the rear of the business, making it
OL,15,Fimpossible for the food business to
OL,16,Fclean effectively or check for the
OL,17,Factivity of pests.
