OL,3,CButchers to stay shut after severe rat
OL,4,Cinfestation found
OL,6,FCouncil officers also described the
OL,7,Fcondition of the walk-in chillers as
OL,8,Ffilthy, with rotting food debris on
OL,9,Fthe floor surfaces underneath plastic
OL,10,Fpallets.
OL,12,FA bag of raw meat was being stored
OL,13,Fdirectly on top of a crate of avocados
OL,14,Fand open raw meat was observed being
OL,15,Fstored directly on the floor surface
OL,16,Fof the walk-in freezer.
