OL,3,CButchers to stay shut after severe rat
OL,4,Cinfestation found
OL,6,FRat activity is a serious risk to
OL,7,Fcustomers' health due to the pests
OL,8,Furinating and defecating on surfaces
OL,9,Fand food items - they can carry
OL,10,Fseveral diseases that can be harmful
OL,11,Fto humans.
OL,13,FDuring the visit, council officers
OL,14,Fserved a Hygiene Emergency Prohibition
OL,15,Fnotice formally closing the business.
OL,17,FThe store is owned by Kenya Butchers
OL,18,FSwindon Limited and the business did
OL,19,Fnot to attend court.
