OL,3,CButchers to stay shut after severe rat
OL,4,Cinfestation found
OL,6,FThe emergency prohibition order
OL,7,Fgranted by magistrates allows the
OL,8,FCouncil to keep the shop shut until it
OL,9,Fis satisfied that the safety of
OL,10,Fcustomers can be met.
OL,12,FThe owners of the business will have
OL,13,Fto contact the Council if they believe
OL,14,Fthe risks to human health are under
OL,15,Fcontrol and an environmental health
OL,16,Fofficer will attend immediately to
OL,17,Fwork with the food business to ensure
OL,18,Fconditions are safe for it to reopen.
OL,20,FMagistrates awarded the Council full
OL,21,Fcosts of #3,493.70.
