OL,6,FCouncillor Jim Grant, Swindon Borough
OL,7,FCouncil's Cabinet Member for Joint
OL,8,FWorking and Communities, says: "The
OL,9,Fconditions found in this business were
OL,10,Fshocking as you can see from the
OL,11,Fpictures our food hygiene officers
OL,12,Ftook.
OL,14,F"Cases like this are rare but, when
OL,15,Fthey do occur, our officers will take
OL,16,Faction straight away to protect the
OL,17,Fhealth and safety of the public.
